      • newMySQLConfig

        public static IMySQLConfiguration newMySQLConfig(String host,
                                                 int port,
                                                 String base,
                                                 String user,
                                                 String pass,
                                                 String tableName)
        Create a new MySQL configuration link instance.
        Parameters:
        host - The MySQL connection host name.
        port - The MySQL connection port.
        base - The name of the MySQL base.
        user - The user name used to connect to the base.
        pass - The user password.
        tableName - The name of the table to access.
        Returns:
        Returns a MySQL configuration abstraction.

        Create a new MySQL configuration section link instance.

        base - The name of the MySQL base.
        user - The user name used to connect to the base.
        pass - The user password.
        tableName - The name of the table to access.
        path - The configuration section path.

      • newSubConfig

        public static IConfiguration newSubConfig(Configurations.ConfigurationType type,
                                          IConfiguration root,
                                          String path)
        Gets a configuration sub-section at the given path.
        Parameters:
        type - The type of the configuration.
        root - The configuration parent section.
        path - The path relative to the `root` section.
        Returns:
        Returns a configuration sub-section.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - If `root` is a flat configuration type (flat = no sections).
        IllegalArgumentException - If `type` is MySQL or FlatMySQL (they need special arguments).
